messages.content: I forgot to mention last night: I'm trying to raise money for a bicycle fundraiser in August. It's for cystic fibrosis, which my sister got diagnosed with last year. You can donate to one of the riders on our team if you want. Or you can sign up for the race. It's August 20 in Ann Arbor, $25 to sign up. Should be fun. I'm trying to get Coop and some other GV people to do it. You can sign up for 30 or 60 mile ride. Here's the websites if you're interested:
Thanks. I'm back in Michigan for at least the next year. I'll probably be on the east side of the state most of the year. But I'll let you know next time I come over this way.
Hey! mine is 616-406-4779. Are you back for good now?
Kyle, are you living around GR? I'm gonna be there this weekend. Just wondering if you wanna hang out. At any rate, text me so I have your number; I lost my phone. My number's still the same. Andy
